title: 9 - Corey Haim: Lost Years of the Lost Boy
description: Corey Haim went one from a teen heartthrob and one of the most bankable child stars of the late 80s to being a junkie and out-of-work actor labeled as a “has been” by the early 90s to being virtually homeless before he was thirty. Find out what happened to Dan’s onetime favorite actor in this tragic (and fascinating) edition of Timesuck!
author: dan@dancummins.tv (Dan Cummins)
